assessment.agree_question_description:
Nres thiab hu rau kev pab xwm ceev thaum koj ntsib tej yam no:
• Mob hauv siab heev
• Ua pa nyuaj heeev
• Dias taub hau heev
• Tsis meej pem heev lossis tsis teb
assessment.agree_question_text: Qhov no puas yog ib qho xwm ceev?
assessment.agreement_cta: Kuv nkag siab thiab tso cai
assessment.agreement_description: Qhov kev ntsuas no yog pab koj txiav txim seb qhov kev kho mob twg tsim nyog rau koj. Nws tsis yog kev ntsuas kho mob lossis rau lwm yam.
assessment.agreement_footer: Yog koj txuas mus ntxiv, ces twb yog koj txaus siab rau tej kev ntsuas no thiab yuav tsis coj los siv kho koj tus mob.
assessment.agreement_title: Qhov no tsis yog kev ntsuas kho mob
assessment.caregiver_description:
Mus qhia ib tus kws kho mob nyob hauv koj lub tsev tu neeg mob sijhawm ntev. Kev nyob hauv ib lub tsev tu neeg mob sijhawm ntev lossis tsev laus kuj yuav ua rau qhov kis tau mob siab dua.  

Qhia rau ib tus tu neeg mob tias koj mob lawm thiab xav mus ntsib ib tus kws kho mob kom sai li sai tau.
assessment.caregiver_title: Mus Qhia Tus Tu Neeg Mob
assessment.complete_description: Qhov koj qhia txog koj tus kheej li mob thiab tau tawm rooj mus twg rau koj lub zej zog yam tsis tas qhia koj npe, twb yog koj nqis tes pab tiv thaiv tus kab mob COVID-19 txhob nthuav dav.
assessment.complete_title: Mus Qhia Tus Tu Neeg Mob!
assessment.distancing_description: Thov ua raws li koj lub zos, xeev, lossis tsoom fwv loj tej txheem lus hais koj sib cais deb thiab siv cov cuab yeej tiv thaiv ntiag tus (Personal Protection Equipment, PPE) xws li looj lub npog ntsej muag thiab/lossis hnab looj tes. Tsis tas yuav dabtsi ntxiv rau lub sijhawm no.
assessment.distancing_title: Kev Sib Cais Deb thiab PPE
assessment.emergency_description: Raws li koj cov tsos mob, koj yuav tsum mus cuag kev kho mob tam sim no.
assessment.emergency_title: Hu mus rau Kev Pab Cuam Xwm Ceev
assessment.experiencing_any_symptoms: muaj tej tsos mob zoo li no
assessment.experiencing_some_symptoms: muaj tej txhia tsos mob zoo li no
assessment.isolate_description: Koj muaj tej tsos mob uas tej zaum yog kab mob COVID-19. Hu mus rau koj tus kws kho mob yog tias koj cov tsos mob tsuas muaj phem zuj zus. Pib cais nyob ib leeg hauv tsev.
assessment.share_cta: Kuv nkag siab thiab tso cai
assessment.share_cta_skip: Kav liam, kuv tsis xav tso tawm kuv li ntaub ntawv
assessment.share_description:
Koj li ntaub ntawv yam tsis qhia tawm koj npe yuav pab cov {{authority}} ntsuas, soj qab, thiab tswj tus kab mob COVID-19. Koj li ntaub ntawv yuav muab sib xyaw nrog cov sab nraud uas siv PathCheck thiab txaus siab tso tawm ib yam.

Koj li ntaub ntawv yog tej uas rub los ntawm cov lus nug thiab tus zauv cheeb tsam, tiamsis yuav tsis qhia tso tawm koj npe thiab tej ntaub ntawv txuam nrog koj npe.

Lub {{authority}} yuav ceev tseg koj li ntaub ntawv rau ib lub sijhawm.
assessment.share_title: Tso tawm ntaub ntawv tsis muaj npe
assessment.start_description: Koj li ntaub ntawv yuav khaws cia zoo thiab tsis qhia tawm. Txhua yam yuav tsis pub tso tawm yam tsis tau koj kev tso cai.
assessment.start_title: Teb cov lus nug txog koj li tsos mob thiab keeb kwm kev kho mob los mus kawm txog seb yuav ua li cas txog tus kab mob COVID-19

onboarding.privacy_policy: Kev Cai Txog Kev Ceev Ntiag Tug
onboarding.protect_privacy_button: Peb tiv thaiv koj ntaub ntawv li cas

protect_privacy.body_1: Tej naj npawb no tsis muaj koj li ntaub ntawv nyob rau hauv thiab yuav hloov txhua 10-20 feeb kom thiaj li tiv thaiv tau koj.
protect_privacy.body_2: Tej xov tooj yuav hloov naj npawb nrog lwm lub xov tooj uas siv Bluetooth Low Energy thiab. Ua li no lub {{applicationName}} thiaj li soj qab tau koj mus nyob ze leejtwg yam tsis tas qhia npe, thiab tab txawm koj twb tsis qhib lub app siv hauv koj xov tooj.
protect_privacy.body_3: Tom qab koj kuaj yog mob COVID-19 lawm, cov neeg siv yuav tso tawm tus naj npawb mus rau {{applicationName}} kom nias meej tias yeej yog lawv mob tiag tiag. Yog lawv ua li no, ces lawv lub xov tooj tus naj npawb uas tsim los ntawd yuav muab cim tseg thiab xa mus rau lub twj ntsuas kuaj. Qhov ua li thiaj li pab cheem lwm tus neeg dag tias nws mob.
protect_privacy.header: Peb tiv thaiv koj ntaub ntawv li cas
protect_privacy.subheader_2: Cov xov tooj uas taws qhov proximity tracing yuav sib hloov cov naj npawb no nrog lwm lub xov tooj uas nws tau mus ze

onboarding.proximity_tracing_body1: Yog tias cov xov tooj uas muaj lub app nyob hauv thiab muab taws, muaj Bluetooth, thiab nyob sib ze rau ib lub sijhawm twg, ces yuav cuv cia tias tau mus raug nyob rau hauv koj lub xov tooj.
onboarding.proximity_tracing_body2: Nyob rau lub sijhawm koj mus raug nws, koj tej ntaub ntawv yuav tsis qhia tawm rau nws paub. Lub app no tsis ceev tseg koj ntaub ntawv ntiag tug. Tsuas yog cov naj npawb hloov mus hloov los random ID xwb. Tej no yuav muab lwv tawm li ntawm 14 hnub.
